{"tid":689400,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"我覺得反對去深圳食野既連登仔都係盲反","createTime":"2018-06-04T05:00:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-04T14:25:28.000Z","uid":12599,"like":3,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a40216029e838e35ac072787a111ba14e8154fe2","tid":689400,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T05:00:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/1730452040432608/?fref=mentions\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcablechinadesk%2Fvideos%2F1730452040432608%2F%3Ffref%3Dmentions&d=kdpm3TGC%2FPzajP3Vx6HhkEkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=a4020ea3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/1730452040432608/?fref=mentions</a><br />\n<br />\n【觸目驚心火鍋店】 【火鍋油重用 水杯地拖一齊洗 剩菜回收】<br />\n<br />\n在全國有600百多間加盟店的小龍坎老火鍋，被爆出三間分店有食物安全問題，衛生惡劣。<br />\n<br />\n【吉林長春歐亞店】<br />\n●把客人吃剩的湯底拿回廚房隔出火鍋油，重新提煉，變成紅當當的「口水油」<br />\n●客人投訴肉品有怪味，待應就用豬血蘸一下，「上上色」<br />\n<br />\n【黑龍江哈爾濱會展店】<br />\n●回收客人吃剩的餸菜<br />\n<br />\n【江西南昌店】<br />\n●喝水的杯子與拖把用同一個盆洗，職員表示，「沒有盆，用開水燙一下就好」<br />\n<br />\n小龍坎老火鍋發聲明回應，指涉事的三間分店已停業調查，會加強監管所有分店，又堅持油只可以使用一次，歡迎社會各界參觀廚房。<br />\n<br />\n#小龍坎火鍋<br />\n#口水油<br />\n#好恐怖<br />\n#有同事上星期食過<br />\n#唔好嘔<br />\n#有線中國組<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n明明d分店就唔係深圳,點解連登仔要盲反?"},{"pid":"912b43a7099672095e591139cb6f0d58b36a21fd","tid":689400,"uid":59818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T05:30:51.000Z","msg":"負皮錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97dc6b238510d6cdd399a3315b22ff452cbf2aa4","tid":689400,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T14:25:28.000Z","msg":"因住一陣人地整個深圳&ldquo;游&ldquo;你嘆下"}]}